Love the strokes...the only album that didnt blow me away was Angles...
Loved the first three and really liked Comedown Machine.

its just pure ponderous dribble.

The strokes are just doing what software algorithm might do if fed the strokes back catalogue. But I actually think the software could do a better job.

This is a poor album.

BIG Strokes fan here

BUT its just nice to hear my BAND back in these shitty days were in
